    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Brazilian dry-climate general regions far from urban areas. These are inhabited by people such subsistence farmers, and are considered to have their own distinct cultural associations apart from the urban experience, equating to 'country' or 'rural' life.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
